Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.65,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,あのあのどんな色が　今ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.19,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顔のホワイト　涙のブルー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.96,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,重ねてみたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:48.45,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,本日晴天なりっ　キャンパスに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,ミルクのアイス　ラムネごくん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.73,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,元気にカラートッピング
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:57.56,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,おーい！　ラブ描き·ぷりーす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:03.71,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなの似顔絵コンテスト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:10.92,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,よーし！　後で「ぷんっ」怒らないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.05,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,スイッチ押されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.17,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,わっはっは～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:24.49,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかいいキモチ　なればいいカンジ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:28.93,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,競争だ！　いち早くリンゴ食べよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:35.21,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,そうじゃないんだよ　躁でいいんだよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.88,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,果物はモデルさん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:47.94,OP日文,NTP,0,0,0,,さあデッサンしましょうか　宿題だよん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.65,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请问请问　现在是什么颜色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.19,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的白色　泪水的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.96,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,将它们重叠在一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:48.45,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气晴朗　外出郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:50.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,进行冰牛奶弹珠汽水特训
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.73,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,代表精神的颜色正充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:57.56,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,喂－！　喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:03.71,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,请来进行大家的肖像画素描比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:10.92,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,好－吧！　之后可别「砰」的一下就生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.05,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,被人按下按钮时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.17,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:24.49,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得只要开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:28.93,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛吧　看谁苹果吃得快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:35.21,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样　急躁起来好吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.88,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,水果便是模特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:47.94,OP中文,NTP,0,0,0,,来　开始素描吧　这是作业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平时弄习惯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来今天是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:58.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,暖阳庄的门牌  做个新的换上吧\N房东书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,暖阳庄的门牌  做个新的换上吧\N房东书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「8月21日  日本的夏日」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}做门牌的事情\N决定在小宫的房间里\N由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.98,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}发送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打磨成这样行么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微把角磨圆些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}桃月每日新闻\N宫田水坝决堤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把角磨圆？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那就磨得太过了  宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}行贿嫌疑加大\N炸丸子大会开幕\N三味线屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到防水涂料了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫的房间倒是令人意外地整洁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到刚才为止都是没处下脚的状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:04:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又决定在小宫房间里做门牌呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为说到了我的房租比其他人的都要便宜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便宜的话是指多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四零零零零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四零零…四万日圆？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们住一楼都得四万五千日圆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,面积同为八张榻榻米的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且厨房浴室和卫生间都和其他的房间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这202号房间的房租很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是个很大的谜哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猪口山君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时髦侦探甜心巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据我的推理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间搞不好就是人们常说的名声不佳的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名声不佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所谓的「某物」出现的屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,猪口山君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有东西出现…难道是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从前暖阳庄被称作“浴血庄”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.88,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：暖阳为“ひだまり（hidamari）”， 浴血为“ちだまり（chidamari）”，仅仅改动了首字）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:04:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里的房客会一直吵嚷到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以好象也有叫作“闭嘴庄”的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：闭嘴为“おだまり（odamari）”， 和前面一样也是仅仅改动了首字）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么个包袱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：原文为“おち（ochi）”，便是相声里说的包袱，笑料）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,传说暖阳庄的某个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地板浸透了大量的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在走路都会发出吱吱的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听…听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前没听到过那种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许只是寻学姐的体重太过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我可是都没有吃过饭的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从早上开始就什么都没有吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就吃了三个蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才  地板吱的一声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安静下来的话听得很清楚的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人在房间里的时候总是唱歌所以没有注意过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那些偶尔能模糊听见的歌声是小宫在唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也一直唱到晚上大概十一点的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我九点的样子就睡了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学听到的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁在唱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不是我在说梦话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我父母说过我有时会边睡边唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是梦话不如说是梦歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的暑假居然被指派做这种杂活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就凭这么一张纸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要做自己住的公寓的门牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,磨成这样就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快点写字上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照先来后到的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想画什么字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「DA」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「MA」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  「RI」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么「HI」就是我负责了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎地觉得能弄出很个性化的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是这剩下的「庄」由谁来画呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就写「暖阳城堡」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：暖阳城堡为“Chateletひだまり”）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「シャトレ」也能四个人分工写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：“シャトレ”为“Chatelet”的片假名）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「暖阳城堡」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为这个公寓的名字不是太花哨了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么写「暖阳屋」什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：暖阳屋为“Maison ひだまり”， Maison，法语，意为“自己的家”）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是只有七个字么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:38.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：暖阳屋在日语中以假名书写一共七个字）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要么写「暖阳黄金住宅」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:42.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：暖阳黄金住宅为“Golden Heights ひだまり”）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也能分成四份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  一共十二个字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（当然，这里的字数也是假名的个数）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多木板么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改名字不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,选什么颜色好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐是大红色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以寻来说这还真是大胆的用色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在学校碰见吉野屋老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰见老师了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是暑假为什么在学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  寻同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这么热你还穿着厚外套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了新的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就想穿给别人看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候的红色便牢牢地印在我的眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挥之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个打击太大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变态大叔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还附了张图片来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还用手机发泳装图片过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这背景的海不是画么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,画？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:09:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了发来泳装图片居然如此用心良苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师还真是卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来  是不是老师想去海边了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海…大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就弄干它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面涂上防水涂料就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿慰问品来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冰凉的加冰香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和在冰箱里冷藏的香草曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,味道真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉全身舒适  好象被治愈一般了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是寻学姐盆栽的香草么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是栽培得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有些虫害啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总算是有收获了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也种些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,百里香和薄荷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柠檬草和迷迭香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卷心菜和胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洋葱和马铃薯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加到冰淇淋里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加到香草茶里去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做成咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做成回锅肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能放进浴缸里洗澡用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能养养鸡啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优雅的生活\N优雅的饮食生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说来由乃也种了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐难道是说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…请不要说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想起来也是不寒而栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振翅飞去的青虫君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又在哪里做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笔掉在地上就自己滚过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地板难道不平么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是因为寻学姐坐在那里的缘故么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地板翘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:10:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好象这边的地板更高些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你掀起地板做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼看去全是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多像是脆饼干包装里那种干巴巴的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脆饼干包装里那种干巴巴的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干燥剂？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的问题房屋么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宫子  走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到房东那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情不和她说清楚是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,下午的这一个小时打算怎么度过呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小蟹  伊原幸惠和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:41.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,单口相声里大家已经熟识的小山  山下章一将给您带来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,房东是个怎么样的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？由乃你没有见过么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还一次都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为搬来的租约什么的父母全都替我办好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大阪世博会的太阳塔一样的人…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳…塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：太阳塔，1970年大阪世博会会场中展示的\n由冈本太郎制作的艺术建筑，大阪世博会的标志建筑）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是个普通的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还算是美人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美人？就是说是女人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是应该和她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,202号房间的谜也解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宫子的房间为什么房租便宜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回答的机会每人有三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,限制的时间只有5秒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是租约上金额弄错了之类？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因为名声不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非和这翘起来的地板有什么联系？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃这一点提得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再进一步就是答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前住这里的人  在房间里养了什么个头很大的动物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多干燥剂的话就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,养了鳄鱼什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是爬行类而是水生生物么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是海豹或海獭什么的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说怎么会变成那样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  别卖关子了快点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个公寓改建的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中途预算不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只有我的房间是房东自己改建的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么到现在还是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还是这样据她说是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「没有钱的孩子可以很高兴地住进来」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她希望没有什么钱的孩子也能追寻着自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个202号房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是包含着房东这样的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是个感人的故事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,房东上真是个很好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  在地板上洒了太多的水的话也许干燥剂会烧起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她让我们注意些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,台风什么的来了的话也许会漏雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两件事摆在一起看  可就极其危险了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅雨的时候这房间漏过雨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐画的「HI」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫的「DA」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐的「MA」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「RI」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大家一起画的「庄」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  很有视觉冲击的效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我之前想的有点差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做门牌非常有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么的感觉今天好充实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好戏还在后头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:49.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}准备了很多盛大的活动\N大家都积极参加啊\N只有身着浴衣参加的客人\N才能得到作为礼物的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏季庙会？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在房东家拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是拿着这传单去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得到点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,写明了「只有身着浴衣参加的客人」哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.70,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：浴衣（yukata），较薄的和服，多为夏季穿着）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐有么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算是有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,格子花纹的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象可以做个比较时髦的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你不是想现做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全融入夏天  得到点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫你冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这儿有以前穿过的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  找着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面是什么花纹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法少女Minki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡通人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  这样就算穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫穿好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  正合适正合适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是专门为我做的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没想到很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  反而让人觉得很时髦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道只有我看成了[哔－]女了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穿浴衣花了番工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英真是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始像男人一样穿浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  能听见庙会的歌舞声了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢庙会的歌舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听着就有点按捺不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作手机铃声吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作闹铃声什么的也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得作匝道口的声音正合适
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,匝道口？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～庙会庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻  你穿那浴衣的话很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你很小的时候的东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个我只穿过两次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？只两次？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那浴衣稍微有点不大吉利…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不吉利？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次穿上它去庙会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在临时舞台那儿买的章鱼烧居然没有放章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一盒八个都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是灾难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次是高台倒了我被压在底下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  大伙儿  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉…吉野屋老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很平常地穿浴衣来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是吉野屋老师也不能连庙会都穿泳装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  那件浴衣很好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是蔷薇图案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的浴衣也都很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是宫子同学那件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我把这作为今后衣装的参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  第七个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫钓气球很拿手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小时侯没什么钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庙会时给的零花钱一直只有100日圆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便用一次钓上来的气球和小朋友交易各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三个气球可以换一份章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庙会真是太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也成功拿到了点心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有焰火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  「地老鼠」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是挺喜欢玩这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么的它们总是追着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小时侯便让猫猫守在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这些的话总会觉得有些寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也想看看绚丽些的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说寻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那件不吉利的浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还好好地保留着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那件浴衣有狐狸附体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「有祸必有福  好好保存下去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶是这么和我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也许真有点多灾多难的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你还让宫子穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？但是如果由乃穿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那件浴衣有点太合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？小宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,焰火「嘭」的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 压轴烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  那声音听不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来小宫刚才说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:38.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：和下文“键屋”为江户时代起两著名焰火生产商）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,aloha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：aloha为夏威夷土著人的问候语，宫子这里为了压韵在信口胡诌）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是键屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有小宫听得见焰火的声音呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说寻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那果然是受浴衣的影响么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话果真有狐狸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃油炸豆腐包饭卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：此物名亦可作“狐寿司”，不用再多说了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏季庙会真愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小宫一个人听见的焰火的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐说那可能是浴衣有狐狸附体的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干…干什么  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你吃了刨冰么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见「喀嚓喀嚓」做刨冰的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我没有弄出那种声音来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是寻学姐的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刨冰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道的？小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是顺风耳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:21:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实让人觉得被什么东西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8月21日  完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
